take required mutton pieces
half cup of veneger
2 tablespoon of salt
2 spoons of garlic
mix the mutton pieces well
1 teaspoon of ground black pepper
1 tablespoon of paprika
1 table spoon of onion powder
half table spoon of cayenne pepper
mix the all ingrediants with mutton pieces
put all the pieces on grill
put some butter on the top of the mutton pieces
roast them well till pieces become crunchy
done!
